# Repository code ownership for AutoTriage.
#
# GitHub requests a review from the owner(s) when a PR touches matching paths.
# Precedence is "last match wins". This file governs the *repository*; it is
# distinct from the demo app's CODEOWNERS at target/CODEOWNERS that the agent
# uses to assign finding owners (see docs/configuration.md).

# Default owner for everything.
*                       @rohanbatrain

# Source, tests, and packaging.
/src/                   @rohanbatrain
/tests/                 @rohanbatrain
/pyproject.toml         @rohanbatrain

# Documentation and runbooks.
/docs/                  @rohanbatrain
*.md                    @rohanbatrain

# CI, automation, and repo governance.
/.github/               @rohanbatrain

# Evaluation harness and labeled ground truth (triage-quality gate).
/evals/                 @rohanbatrain
